step_data.thought: I previously tried to report that I couldn't find editable fields, but received an error for an empty action. Looking more carefully at the page, I see I'm on the Address Book page. To edit an address, I need to click on one of the 'Change' links. I see two options: 'Change Billing Address' or 'Change Shipping Address'. Since both appear to be for Emily Lopez (rather than Emma Lopez as mentioned in the goal), and both show the same address '101 S San Mateo Dr', I'll click on 'Change Billing Address' to access the edit form where I can update the street address to '202 Main St'.
